        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d3">
          <summary>What industries benefit most from GEO in Singapore?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>F&amp;B, professional services, healthcare, education, and beauty are among the industries that benefit most from GEO in Singapore &mdash; any industry where consumers ask AI for recommendations. When someone asks ChatGPT for the best <a href="/restaurant-ai-search-optimisation-singapore/">restaurant</a>, <a href="/clinic-ai-search-optimisation-singapore/">clinic</a>, or <a href="/beauty-salon-ai-search-optimisation-singapore/">salon</a> in Singapore, GEO determines whether your brand is the one that gets named.</p></div>
