          <div class="faq-answer"><p>GEO and <a href="/llmo-services-singapore/">LLMO</a> describe the same discipline. GEO (Generative Engine Optimisation) is the broader term covering all generative AI platforms, while LLMO (Large Language Model Optimisation) specifically references the large language model technology that powers those platforms. In practice, the strategies are identical &mdash; read more in our <a href="#geo-terminology">terminology guide</a> above.</p></div>
